casebody.data:
Marcus B. HARRIS, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Jennifer FOLSOM, Warden, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4355 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. December 06, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's petition for writ of certiorari is denied.

Petitioner's motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis waive fees is denied as moot.

BLACK, SLEET, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
